{ We have sacrificed the exchange but our attack is deadly! } 20... Bxe6 21.
Qf6
{ Blockading the f-pawn and involving the most powerful piece into the attack. }
21... Qg4
{ Black tries to get some counterplay on the kingside, attacking both the e4-Bishop and the g3-pawn. }
