Ne2
{ Developing the last minor piece and intending to castle kingside, attack the Queen either with Bc4 or Nf4 and put more pressure on the e6 pawn. If Black decides to be greedy and take on g2,   13. ...Qxg2  14.Rg1  followed by O-O-O, Bg5, Rg3, Nf4, Bc4 would give Black a hard time. }
