12... Qa5
{ Black decides to involve the Queen in the attack right now, without developing the light-squared Bishop. There is also an interesting idea to open up the queenside with ...b5 on the next move. }
13. h3 { We want to get clarity in the center. } 13... Nxe5 14. Nxe5
{ It's better to have the Bishop on e5, than the Knight, because it will support the attack by putting pressure on the g7-pawn. }
