10. O-O-O { Pinning the d7-Knight and hiding the King. } 10... fxe5 11. Bg5
{ We move the Bishop with tempo. } 11... Qe8 12. Bd3
{ Although Black is a pawn up, their pieces are still not developed and the King is quite exposed. The doubled pawns on the e-file are also weak. In turn, the white Bishops dominate the position. }
