hxg3
{ On the other hand, the h-file opens up, surprisingly activating the Rook without making a single move. }
13... Rf7
{ Although this move is definitely not the best one, I decided to make it the main continuation due to my huge respect for Boris Gelfand, who played it against the former world champion Anatoly Karpov. }
14. g4
{ A good way to launch the attack on the kingside. It would be a disaster for Black to take the g4-pawn as we can take on h7 with the Queen.   14.b4!  is equally good. }
