16. exf5 { Anyway, we should continue our plan. } 16... Rxf5 17. Bd3
{ The Bishop is placed on d3 more actively than on e2. } 17... Rf8 18. Bh7+
{ It's a good idea to force Black to move the King to the same file with the h1-Rook. }
18... Kh8 19. Be4
{ We want to play Qd2, putting more pressure on the h6-pawn, as well as on the d7-pawn. }
