12. Be2
{ We should develop our pieces first. It's dangerous to play actively with the King in the center. }
12... Rc8
{ Black is x-raying our Queen now.   12. ...Be7  13.Nb5  Nxg3  14.hxg3  transposes to  11. ... Be7     12. ...Nxg3  13.hxg3  Be7  transposes to  11. ... Be7 }
