{ Black wants to win back a pawn as fast as possible.   7. ...a5  Another way to win back the c5-pawn.  8.Bf4  The Bishop is eyeing the tempting d6-square.  8. . ..Na6  9.f3!  Preventing ...Ne4.  9. ...b6  10.Bd6  Occupying a great outpost with tempo.  10. ...Re8  11.cxb6  Qxb6  12.c5+-  Black doesn't have compensation for a pawn.     7. ...Nc6  This is not even an attempt to win back a pawn.  8.Bg5  Pinning the f6-Knight.  8. ...b6  9.cxb6  axb6  10.e3  We're going to finish the development soon and there is no sign of compensation for Black. }
