9... a6 { Black prevents Nb5. } 10. h4 { Preparing g5. } 10... h5
{ Again Black tries to create an outpost for the Knight on g4. } 11. g5 Ng4 12.
a3 { Aiming to grab space with b4 on the next move. } 12... b6 13. b4
{ Driving the c5-Bishop away and liberating the b2-square for the c1-Bishop. }
13... Be7 14. Bb2
{ We're going to centralize the Knight with Ne4, opening the b2-g7 diagonal and attacking the g7-pawn. }
