7... d5 { Black starts fighting for the center. } 8. b4
{ Since Black hasn't prevented b4, why not proceed with our original plan? }
8... Bd6
{ I don't find this move logical as it only helps us to execute our original plan. }
9. c5
{ Winning space and creating the pawn majority on the queenside with tempo now. }
9... Bc7 10. Bg5 { Pinning the Knight and preventing .. .e5 at the same time. }
