12. bxc3 Rxb8 13. f3
{ According to my base, this is a novelty, although it's the only move, which clearly wins. }
13... Ng3 { A discovered double attack. } 14. Qa4+
{ I suppose the reason why f3 wasn't played is that players missed this wonderful idea. An intermediate check! }
14... Bd7 15. Qd4
{ One more intermediate attack! After   15. ...Nxh1  16.Qxh8  Ke7  17.Qxh6  I hardly believe the h1-Knight can ever escape. }
