{ Unpinning the c3-Knight and thereby threatening to win the black Queen. }
7... Bxc3 8. Bxc3
{ We have a long-term strategic advantage now - a Bishop pair. } 8... b6
{ Intending to develop a Bishop to b7, where it will be much more active than on d7. }
9. e3 { We should complete our development. } 9... Bb7 10. Be2 Nbd7
{ It's too early for Black to play ...c5, as the f6-Knight hasn't been protected yet. }
