{ Transferring a Bishop to an open diagonal. } 12... c5
{ Black should jump at the opportunity to play ...c5 right now, otherwise, it can be too late.   12. ...Rfd8  13.Rfd1!  X-raying the black Queen and preventing ...c5. }
