{ We continue chasing it and kick it out of the center. } 14... Ng6 15. Bd2
{ Protecting the f4-pawn and aiming to start an attack on the kingside as soon as possible. }
15... a6 { In turn, Black wants to create counterplay with ...b5. } 16. h4
{ We give up the g4-square but instead, we get great prospects on the kingside. }
