13... h6 14. Bh4 { Maintaining the pin. } 14... Re8 15. Ne4
{ Exploiting the pin to attack the weak d6-pawn. } 15... Qe7 16. N2g3
{ We transfer the Knight to f5 and aim to occupy the open b-file with Rab1, followed by a3. Black's position is hopeless. }
