{ 12. ...b6  is a logical way to develop a light-squared Bishop.  13.Nd2  Threatening Bf3 and looking for the best square for a Knight.  13. ...Bb7  14.Rac1  Improving a Rook.  14. ...Rfe8  15.Nf1  Transferring a Knight to g3, followed by Nf5 at some point. }
13. Nd2 Re8 14. f3 { Depriving Black of a space advantage in the center. }
